Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:20.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:26.18,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand
