Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:36.94,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that\Nsomething is about to change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:42.26,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you\Ncalling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:48.87,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking up at cloudy skies,\NI sense what's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:56.90,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reach out our hands\Nwith courage stronger than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:02:01.84,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and shadow are both still far off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:08.18,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, we want to know\Nthe reason for this kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:15.64,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look now, beyond the brilliance\Nthat goes by nobody's name
