Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:33.54,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayuko has logged in."\N"Please insert name here has logged in."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.94,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayuko: Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:38.82,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayuko: It's all because\NI made the script like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.50,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here: It's okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:46.97,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"It may not have been the movie\Nyou were hoping for, though."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.89,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayuko: That's not true."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.14,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayuko: What I was hoping for"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:53.50,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayuko: was to cheer with\Neveryone when it was done."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.13,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to say, you\Nreally are something else"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.60,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nah, never mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.07,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪ has logged in."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:06.95,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪ has logged in."\N"Please insert name here has logged in."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:07.78,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here: Hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:08.95,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here: Hello."\N"M-e-♪: Yoo-hoo."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.57,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪: Sounds like it went well."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.52,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here:\NThanks to you, Senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:13.45,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here: However, I"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.08,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here: think I did\Nsomething inexcusable to him."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.74,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"♪: Do you really think that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:22.99,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here: It's no use trying to\Nbluff someone on the other side of the world, is it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.55,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪: Of course not."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:29.21,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪: So, no lying to someone\Non the other side of the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:32.55,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lying, you say?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:36.59,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"You didn't ask for my help because you\Nwanted to protect the scriptwriter, did you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:41.44,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"♪: The whole problem in the first place\Nwas that the script was dull, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:46.10,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"♪: You wanted to reject a script that fell flat\Nin a way that wouldn't hurt that girl, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.60,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"♪: Well, it doesn't sound like\Nthe dummy caught on, anyhow."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.25,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I wasn't in"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.04,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"any position to"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:57.55,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"let the project"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.50,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"fail"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:02.28,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I wasn't very well in any position\Nto let the project fail."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:11.76,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Senpai?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:15.71,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪ has logged out."
